Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉平 这儿都是你的老熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说说吧 谁主使你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}国贼 国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你原本有十根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么变成九个了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嚼指为誓 誓 誓杀国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好一个嚼指为誓 来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在 在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将他剩下的手指全部斩去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看他还有何可嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏 喏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就是没了手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍然有口可以吞贼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有舌可以骂贼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}割掉他的舌头 砸掉他的牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董承
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的病可好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来 一剂药还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还得再来一剂 来呀 带上来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庆童 把你听到的 给大伙说说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴 奴才遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前天晚上 奴才经过主子的上房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在窗外听见主子和太医吉平商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}商量要在丞相的汤药里下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贱奴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}骂得好 这个奴才是贱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹贼 事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我别无所求 只求速死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不急 不急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都不着急 你着什么急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还有话要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庆童 你的主子说你贱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自个儿说 你贱不贱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奴才 奴 奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你贱 因为你犯了两条大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其一 身为奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你却与主子的小妾通奸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二 你身为奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却隔窗偷听主子谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这还不算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还跑来向我告密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这不是卖主求荣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这两桩大罪的任何一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都可以让你碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董承 看来你是有眼无珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然养出这等奴才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不如养一条赖皮狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻把这个奴才拉下去 斩首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 我救了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何还要杀我呀 丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饶命啊 丞相 饶命啊 丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}列位都看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曹操虽狠却正邪分明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们说对不对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相说得极是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}董承 拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把玉带诏拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么玉带诏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是陛下藏在玉带里的血诏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你以为我不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有 万万没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是在董承府中搜出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这都是 拿指血签的名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}车骑将军董承 西凉太守马腾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长水校尉种辑 左将军刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然有这个奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我非得把他碎尸万段不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱妃 皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱妃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 董承谋反你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}破指修诏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这么快就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是我做的事 不关陛下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然是你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是董承的女儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们父女合谋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 请听臣的一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这回的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只处置董妃一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果还有下回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就跟陛下有关了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿 爱卿 董妃已有身孕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能不能等她生下皇子 再
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是想让那个逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将来为母报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下知道她是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她是爱卿的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕的曹妃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下喜欢她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜欢就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}中宫不可空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下不可无后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹妃贤德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请陛下立曹妃为后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕 册封曹妃为中宫皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吾皇万岁 万岁 万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻 发兵徐州 剿灭刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灭刘之后 迎战袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣刘备泣血拜祭祖宗天灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷不幸 国贼肆虐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贵妃惨遭荼毒 忠臣饮恨九泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备上不能安邦兴国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下不能剿贼除害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}苦渡日月 痛断肝肠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备谨此焚香告天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣与那曹贼誓不两立
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宁愿赴汤蹈火 也必手刃奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 曹军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糜芳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将只等主公令下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 估计袁绍大军也距此不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你进入袁军大营后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要先去见袁绍 去见许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸乃袁绍心腹谋臣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}举足轻重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你见到他后跟他道明原委
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得到他的支持以后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再去见袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此把握会更大些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}善战者 一往无前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}善谋者 瞻前顾后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此次出征 丞相动用了全部精锐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兖州几乎是一座空城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据哨探报 袁绍的数十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经进驻官渡 虎视兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果袁绍聪明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令数万疑兵在正面牵制我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己亲率劲旅 急攻我们的后方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}则许昌堪危啊 一旦许昌有失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们将败无可归失去根据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此一招 对袁绍难道不是上策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}确实是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但对袁绍来讲那就未必了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍是个多疑寡断之主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他进而畏惧 退而贪利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临敌时 是五分把握他不战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七分把握也不战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非等到十分把握了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他才全力一战 军机瞬息万变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪有十分把握的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我料 如果丞相在十日之内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿下徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍他不敢轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕我直言 你看徐州城如此坚实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十日之内能拿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能 再者 袁绍多疑寡断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可他身边不乏智谋之士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰 许攸等人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道看不出胜机所在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们不会建议袁绍回攻兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就看我们的兖州将士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能够坚守到多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果坚守到丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能一举攻下徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们就是南北双线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}双获胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果不能的话那就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:17:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 如果拿不下这徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们将退无根据 陷入险境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用兵就是用险 无险就无胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相如果现在要不取徐州城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么日后要取徐州的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备他必定要偷袭许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日后之险 大于今日之险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱有谋略 荀彧有见识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们二人的话我听了都颇受教益
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们知道吗 想当年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍做十八路诸侯盟主的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对董卓就是畏首畏尾 迁延不进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此可见 袁绍兵多 却是庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备兵少 却有雄才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若要战胜袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须得先行攻取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你本是我的囊中物 池中鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只因我一时疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才让你偷得徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操 你名为汉相 实为汉贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备与天下英雄都已奉旨讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誓必杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天底下想杀我的人多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惜都成了冢中枯骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是赶快献城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会给你一片地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让你继续种韭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则破城之时 鸡犬不留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军虽少 却兵精将勇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你兵马虽多 却必败无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你何以如此自大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为袁绍已举大军奔袭足下后方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几日后 定会攻陷许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}试问足下 那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是入黄土呢还是下九泉哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你对袁绍的估计过高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我对足下估计过高了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我原以为你心再毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也当有一丝人伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不至于杀害贵妃 没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你竟然绞死了怀胎的贵妃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让自己的女儿僭位中宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可见你禽兽不如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你当真要战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战至最后一息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是左将军刘备的使臣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公差我进见参军许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说 那曹操曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}亲统二十万兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在攻打徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 徐州万急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公请袁公快快发兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万急 你的意思是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你家主公刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经守不住城池了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不 徐州固若金汤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}激战正酣哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好一个固若金汤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直说吧 糜芳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备尚能支撑多少时日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}百日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五十日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕也多说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许先生啊 我家主公的原话是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他定战至最后一人 最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主公说 许先生满腹韬略
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在袁公驾前是一言九鼎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有说先请许先生准了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才能让袁公进军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你家主公真是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一字不差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实话跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这儿正等着他攻打徐州呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这该如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝等在这儿说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小公子病了 主公焦虑万分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等都不敢进去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都与我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}苍天哪 苍天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这这这 这可怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下许攸 拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸啊 小儿突然患病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命垂危 我可怎么办哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公勿忧 少公子定无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一点小疾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 我们的胜机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么胜机呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方才刘备派糜芳前来报信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是那曹操正亲统二十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在攻打徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如此一来 那许昌定然空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公立刻挥师东进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一举荡平许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹贼一旦失去了根据
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势必大乱啊 而且
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可以顺手牵羊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺势迎取天子 从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这挟天子以令诸侯的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可就是主公你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下指日可待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那许昌有多远哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不会连许昌有多远都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才二百五十里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我儿现在一步都走不动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪走得了二百多里哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 我没说让少公子前去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是恳请主公你派兵奇袭许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你就快快下令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我儿是我的掌上明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他要有不测 我也就不活了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这兵法云
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}机不可失 时不再来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灭曹完全在此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时不我待 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.34,0:24:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下恳求你快快发兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心乱如麻 我神魂颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还打什么仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.86,0:24:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我儿如有不测 我也就不活了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.27,0:24:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你醒醒行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.77,0:24:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.67,0:24:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.35,0:25:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.66,0:25:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁公何时发兵哪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸主啊 庸主啊 庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.77,0:25:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然为了一个孺子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贻误了这么好的战机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.28,0:25:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃亘古奇闻哪 庸主 庸主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.55,0:25:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸辱我 杖二十军棍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸主 庸 庸 庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.16,0:25:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是个庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸 庸主 庸主 庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.08,0:26:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是个庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.25,0:26:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.85,0:26:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已经被围五六天了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.85,0:26:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.66,0:26:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哨骑报 徐州城日夜激战
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.16,0:26:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}城关面前全是曹军的死尸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.76,0:26:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操是有备而来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.36,0:26:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果曹军伤亡巨大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.27,0:26:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怕是主公的伤亡也少不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.17,0:26:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是城池还在主公手里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.37,0:26:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}估计数日后 袁绍就该出兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公坚持不了数日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.45,0:26:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样 我率兵出城偷袭曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.56,0:26:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或许能解徐州之围
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.86,0:26:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下邳城就交你把守
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.56,0:26:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝对不可
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.06,0:27:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军难道忘了主公的军令了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.47,0:27:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只可坚守 不可出战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.17,0:27:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公正在血战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.77,0:27:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我岂能站在这里看着
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.77,0:27:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 整个下邳城里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.27,0:27:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有八千守军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使你全部带出去攻袭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.48,0:27:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也无济于事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.98,0:27:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相反 如果不出战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.08,0:27:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操就不知虚实 将军你看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连日来咱们牵制了曹军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.85,0:27:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五 六万人马
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.86,0:27:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们之所以不敢妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.36,0:27:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是提防将军你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 主公的军令是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.76,0:27:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不出战比出战的作用更大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.27,0:27:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样 我只率两千骑兵偷袭曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.98,0:27:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打着我的旗号守城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.98,0:27:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我偷袭得手即刻回来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.78,0:27:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝不恋战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.38,0:27:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我受命监军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.78,0:27:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果将军执意要出城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.45,0:27:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就从我尸体上踏过去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 糜将军回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.58,0:28:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糜将军回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.05,0:28:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.76,0:28:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伤着没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.16,0:28:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.67,0:28:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍发兵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.37,0:28:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍他不肯发兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.57,0:28:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍 他 他小儿病了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.17,0:28:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他心思恍惚 无心作战哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.78,0:28:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他小儿病了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:28:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大敌当前 生死关头
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.58,0:28:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他身为统帅岂能为一介小儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.58,0:28:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贻误戎机
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.68,0:29:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是在下不亲眼看见
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.18,0:29:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不敢相信哪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.59,0:29:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是袁绍他就偏偏这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.76,0:29:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那许攸可是个明白人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.86,0:29:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他劝了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}劝了 袁绍就是不听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他就大喊什么 庸主 庸主
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.17,0:29:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后还被袁绍打了二十军棍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.47,0:29:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这等主公啊 还不如个婆娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.47,0:29:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上了战场啊他也得尿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 咱们不求他相助
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.58,0:29:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们自个儿也能打退曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.46,0:29:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糜芳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.26,0:29:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.56,0:29:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操把徐州城围得像铁桶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.36,0:29:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎么进城的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.46,0:29:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奇怪啊主公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.06,0:29:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我本来没指望能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.17,0:29:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我潜到城关下一看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.77,0:29:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到处都是死尸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.87,0:29:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 曹军他撤围了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.57,0:29:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.27,0:29:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撤围了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.47,0:29:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.28,0:29:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当真
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.18,0:30:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当真 撤围三十里外
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.18,0:30:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扎下了几座大营
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.79,0:30:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来曹操连日攻城 伤亡惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.09,0:30:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是想休息调整
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.66,0:30:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}养足军力以利再战
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.46,0:30:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他扎的几座大营
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.26,0:30:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定在要道口上 对否
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.96,0:30:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 主公要是突围
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们仍可迎头阻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.17,0:30:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.37,0:30:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操的军力已经是不支了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以他才退得远远的了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们呀 要抓住这个时机
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.98,0:30:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁夜奇袭曹军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.48,0:30:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定可大胜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.49,0:30:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.19,0:30:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍是没有指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.76,0:30:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只能靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.96,0:30:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若等曹操养足军力
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.36,0:30:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就更没有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.27,0:30:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有夜出奇兵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.77,0:30:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方能有几分胜机
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.17,0:31:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.37,0:31:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不就是这么说得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.17,0:31:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传令
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.27,0:31:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各营三更造饭 四更出城
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.38,0:31:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人衔枚 马裹蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.38,0:31:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直袭曹操中军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.58,0:31:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若能攻杀曹操本人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.78,0:31:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此役便可胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.38,0:31:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得令
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.19,0:31:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.67,0:31:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊 依照兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我军远来 利在速战
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.37,0:31:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可你为何要撤军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.68,0:31:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非是主公觉得伤亡太大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.98,0:31:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有些担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.08,0:31:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那五千多具尸首
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.49,0:31:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我有意留在刘备眼皮底下的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.99,0:31:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 这
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.39,0:31:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁哪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.46,0:32:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵法教出来的都是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.87,0:32:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你何时才能成为真正的主将
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.57,0:32:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连日攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.17,0:32:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我用的大多都是弱旅
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.88,0:32:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}精锐部队根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我为何不用
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.08,0:32:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是因为徐州城坚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}强攻伤亡太大
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.19,0:32:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然非伤亡不可
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.99,0:32:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我就留给刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.49,0:32:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几千具弱旅的尸首
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.29,0:32:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备看到城下尸首密布
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.67,0:32:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他肯定会想 曹军乏力了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.87,0:32:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撤军三十里休整
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.07,0:32:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}于是 他会怎么样 你说
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.98,0:32:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他肯定会趁夜劫营
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.39,0:33:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那几千具尸首换来的战机
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.30,0:33:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们必须要把刘备引出城
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.60,0:33:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才能消灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.77,0:33:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.97,0:33:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今明两夜 尤其是今夜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.48,0:33:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必加倍提防
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.78,0:33:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至于如何设伏 交你安排
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.09,0:33:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.49,0:33:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.60,0:34:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 你看哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.50,0:34:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操是毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.20,0:34:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们杀进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.10,0:34:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.10,0:34:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何连巡逻的哨骑都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.47,0:34:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操一向军纪严明
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.38,0:34:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能连哨骑都不设啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.79,0:34:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你看 那两个哨骑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.19,0:34:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来曹军上下都疲惫过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.00,0:34:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 杀进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翼德 子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.87,0:35:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们看见那座大帐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.18,0:35:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那定是曹操中军所在
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.98,0:35:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在令你们不顾一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.68,0:35:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冲过去 如能斩杀曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.48,0:35:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.29,0:35:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.59,0:35:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}举火 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.20,0:36:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这帐内空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.70,0:36:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公这里也没人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.98,0:36:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好 中计了 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.69,0:36:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你个贼曹操 快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.91,0:36:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贼将休走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.88,0:36:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是中军主将曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.28,0:36:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 你中了我家主公计了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.99,0:36:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快快下马受死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.60,0:37:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁小贼 爷爷在此呢 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.60,0:37:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.70,0:37:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公快走 我挡住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.69,0:37:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.59,0:38:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公你神机妙算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.96,0:38:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备跑不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.99,0:38:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里大局已定 走吧许褚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.29,0:38:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随我去取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.41,0:40:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}列祖列宗 刘备无能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.99,0:40:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢问上面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.69,0:40:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是大汉皇叔刘备刘玄德乎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.20,0:40:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘将军你乃擎天之玉柱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.61,0:40:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}架海之津梁
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这匡扶汉室 汝责无旁贷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.11,0:40:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安可轻生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来来来 在下许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.32,0:40:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这厢有理了
